title: Art and Love-An Illustrated Anthology of Love Poetry (Art Ebook)
description:
Art & Love. An Illustrated Anthology of Love Poetry
Metropolitan | 1990 | ISBN: 0821217712 | English | 184 pages | PDF | 24.3 MB

Romantic love, family love, platonic love, lost love, ideal love, troubled love... Throughout the ages great poets have written about the many sides of love and great artists have depicted its power and beauty. Now love poetry and treasures from The Metropolitan Museum of Art have been united in this elegant new anthology. The results are inspired
